ISIBAYA actress Nomzamo Mbatha will represent SA at the African Studies Association (ASA) 59th annual meeting in Washington DC this week.The Kwamashu-born actress flew out of the country yesterday ahead of her scheduled appearance where she will address more than 2 000 global delegates, scholars and professionals at Marriott Wardman Park.Akin Omotoso s film Tell Me Sweet Something, which is one of her recent films will also form part of the screening. On this film I worked with one of the most selfless producers, Akin Omotoso, who imparted that it was never just about his vision, it was a collective effort of all involved, the actress said.-SIYABONGA SITHOLE